pageContext.claim: “They [MS-13] came here over years, and they've taken over towns in Long Island and other places. They're bad people. And we're doing tremendous -- I mean, we're doing big numbers. They don't like Donald Trump, I can tell you that.”
pageContext.analysis: It's a huge exaggeration to say American towns are being "liberated" from MS-13, or that MS-13 has "taken over" towns, as Trump often claims.
